## Quickstart

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate          # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt    # or: pip install -e .
pytest -q                          # unit tests
python simulation/simulator.py     # runs every scenario, writes outputs/
python -m http.server 8080         # then open dashboard/index.html
```

